    "longBusinessSummary": "Thien Long Group Corporation, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and trades in stationery products under Bizner, FlexOffice, Colokit, Diem 10, and TL brands in Vietnam and internationally. The company offers ballpoint, fountain, and rollerball pens, as well as pencils; art supplies, such as colored crayons, oil pastels, colored plastic crayons, colored pencils, colored fiber pens, watercolors, modelling doughs, and coloring books; writing instruments and office supplies, including gel pens, fine liners, papers, file covers, tapes, pastes, and other products; and school supplies comprising boards, chalks, rulers, compasses, erasers, scissors, and notebooks. It also provides classroom equipment, plastic teaching instruments, plastic household appliances, stamps printing, tampo printing, flexo printing, and printing and pressing on products. Thien Long Group Corporation was founded in 1981 and is headquartered in Ho Chi Minh City, Vietnam.",
